is a solution in search of a problem. Oh, the problem with <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Social Security</ENAMEX> is
real enough. But "privatization"--the hot policy idea of <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">the season</TIMEX>--simply
doesn't address the problem. It's as if you were crawling across the desert,
