<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">week</TIMEX>'s report by a government <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">commission</ENAMEX> on <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Social Security</ENAMEX>, a majority
supported various forms of partial privatization. And lemonade (privatization)
